        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.spells.Item.Eldritch Bond]</p>\n<p>You gain up to two of the following abilities:</p><ul><li>Darkvision</li><li>Mental resistance equal to half your level (minimum 1)</li><li>A tentacle unarmed attack that deals bludgeoning damage</li><li>A stinger unarmed attack that deals acid damage and has the agile and finesse traits</li><li>A beam ranged unarmed attack with a range increment of 40 feet that deals mental damage</li><li>10-foot reach on all melee attacks (including the above)</li><li>Melee strikes (including those above) affect incorporeal creatures as if they had the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.equipment.Item.Ghost Killer] upgrade.</li></ul>"
